And I confess to being a fan of the recent TV series Game of Thrones. 
The flat was bought with my son in mind as he attends Edinburgh University, so it is let out during summer and more particularly the Festival period before the academic year starts back in September. That said it is a good step up from usual student accommodation and is a great wee flat, furnishings and decor are more basic than a full time home, but very clean, warm, everything you could need is in the flat  and it is such a great location.

There are also lots of smaller quirky attractions such as the Fashion and Textiles Museum, the Brunel Museum and the Old Operating Theater Museum. host_about:

I love to travel and have visited India, South East Asia, Australia, New Zealand, North America, Peru and Brazil - to name a few! I recently stayed with lovely hosts in Berlin and Istanbul and now would think twice about staying in a hotel!. 

I believe life is about the personal connections we make with people, our friends and families, and the laughter and knowledge we share. I'm lucky to have friends all over the world and have already had many guests from countries such as America, New Zealand, Mexico and the Netherlands. 

I work in the environment field part time but also teach yoga and practice Thai massage. I teach locally and enjoy being part of the Bermondsey community. 

When I'm at home I like reading and writing about yoga, lounging in the hammock, listening to music, art, relaxing, cooking and planning my next adventure. I come from a big family and I really like to share so would be happy to cook a delicious healthy vegetarian meal for you if I'm around. I have two vintage tea sets, and also like to have tea and cake sometimes (very English). Having grown up in London I have a lot of local knowledge and if you need advice just ask, however if you'd just prefer to get lost and wonder around in this amazing city then that's also alot of fun!

I look forward to welcoming you to my little Haven in the center of the city, 

Tania
